name: thebandwithnoname
description: '''thebandwithnoname''' (referred to as "TBWNN" by fans) were a [[Christian music|Christian]] band who were launched by Innervation Trust in March 2002, as their flagship band, alongside girl band [[TBC (band)|TBC]].  TBWNN hosted their final gig at the Stockport Plaza on Saturday 4 September 2010 and have since disbanded.
